My mother said if I passed my road test, she would buy me Tokio Hotel tickets for the Toronto gig at the Mod Club.

Well, I passed my road test. I asked her if she bought the tickets a few days later. She ignored me. I told her that if she didn't get them soon they would be sold out. She told me not to worry about it. This was 2 maybe 3 weeks ago. January 21st ish. it is now February 2nd and she decides to tell me that she could not get the tickets because they were sold out.

I'm sort of extremely pissed, but repressing the fact that I will not be able to see Bill, Tom, Georg and Gustav because there is absolutely nothing I can do about it.
